DDeessccrriippttiioonn
       These routines return the  string  of  characters  in  str
       starting  at the current cursor position in the named win-
       dow  and  ending  at  the  right  margin  of  the  window.
       Attributes  are  stripped  from  the characters.  The four
       functions with n as the last argument return the string at
       most n characters long.

   RReettuurrnn vvaalluueess
       All  routines  return  the integer ERR upon failure and an
       integer value other than ERR upon successful completion.

